[src:sturm-liouville-theory/eigenfunction] which is called the (one-dimensional) wave equation.
[src:sturm-liouville-theory/eigenfunction] Here c is a constant speed that depends on the tension and mass of the string.
[src:sturm-liouville-theory/eigenfunction] This problem is amenable to the method of separation of variables.
